'''Limited''' (制限 ''Seigen'') cards are cards that players are allowed only one copy of in their [[Main Deck]], [[Side Deck]], and [[Extra Deck]] combined. Limited is a [[status]] used in ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Official Card Game]]'', ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Trading Card Game]]'', ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Rush Duel]]'', and ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Master Duel]]''. In the ''TCG'' [[Speed Duel]] format and in ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links]]'', equivalent statuses would be [[Limited 1]] and [[Limited 2]].

