== Anime and manga ==
During the [[Battle City]] tournament, it is stated that players can only have one copy of "[[Monster Reborn (anime)|Monster Reborn]]" in their Decks (ironically, Monster Reborn is also limited to one copy in real life). This influences [[Yami Yugi and Yami Marik's Duel]], in which Yami Marik is forced to recycle his only copy of "Monster Reborn" in order to Special Summon "[[The Winged Dragon of Ra (anime)|The Winged Dragon of Ra]]" from the Graveyard.

